ded to the directive (see: https://github.com/graphql/graphql-spec/issues/300#issuecomment-504734306 and below comments, and https://github.com/graphql/graphql-js/issues/1527)'=>'Estensioni (metadati personalizzati) aggiunte alla direttiva (vedere: https://github.com/graphql/graphql-spec/issues/300#issuecomment-504734306 e commenti successivi, e https://github.com/graphql/graphql-js/issues/1527)','Is this element considered a “sensitive” data element in the schema? (If so, it is only exposed in the schema when \'Expose “sensitive” data elements\' is enabled)'=>'Questo elemento è considerato un elemento di dati "sensibile" nello schema? (In tal caso, viene esposto nello schema solo quando \'Esponi elementi di dati "sensibili"\' è abilitato)','Enum value\'s name as defined by the GraphQL spec (https://graphql.github.io/graphql-spec/draft/#sel-FAJbLACvBBCyBH6rd)'=>'Nome del valore enum come definito dalla specifica GraphQL (https://graphql.github.io/graphql-spec/draft/#sel-FAJbLACvBBCyBH6rd)','Enum value\'s description as defined by the GraphQL spec (https://graphql.github.io/graphql-spec/draft/#sel-FAJbLACyBIC1BHnjL)'=>'Descrizione del valore enum come definita dalla specifica GraphQL (https://graphql.github.io/graphql-spec/draft/#sel-FAJbLACyBIC1BHnjL)','Is the enum value deprecated?'=>'Il valore enum è deprecato?','Why was the enum value deprecated?'=>'Perché il valore enum è stato deprecato?','Extensions (custom metadata) added to the enum value (see: https://github.com/graphql/graphql-spec/issues/300#issuecomment-504734306 and below comments, and https://github.com/graphql/graphql-js/issues/1527)'=>'Estensioni (metadati personalizzati) aggiunte al valore enum (vedere: https://github.com/graphql/graphql-spec/issues/300#issuecomment-504734306 e commenti successivi, e https://github.com/graphql/graphql-js/issues/1527)','The directive type (custom property)'=>'Il tipo di direttiva (proprietà personalizzata)','Include only directives of provided types'=>'Includi solo l